(964, 1, '2014-03-04 11:02:21', '2014-03-04 10:02:21', '<h3><span style="color: #20c3d6;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Working Desks</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n[easy-pricing-table id="972"]\r\n\r\nHourly booking available with <strong><span style="color: #20c3d6;"><a style="color: #20c3d6;" href="http://mobispot.be/fr/public/search/spot-details/74" target="_blank">Mobispot</a></span></strong>\r\n<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #20c3d6;"><strong>Meeting Rooms</strong></span></h3>\r\n[easy-pricing-table id="1016"]\r\nAdditional services can be foreseen on demand (coffee break, lunch...).\r\nPlease contact us for briefing and price offer.\r\n\r\nFor any information regarding availability or booking, please send us an email at <strong><span style="color: #20c3d6;"><a style="color: #20c3d6;" href="p3@factorx.eu">p3@factorx.eu</a></span></strong>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #20c3d6;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Copy/printer</span></strong></span></h4>\r\n- A4 BW : 0,05 €\r\n- A4 Col : 0,50 €\r\n- 43 BW : 0,10 €\r\n- A3 Col : 1,00 €\r\n<h4><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #20c3d6;"><strong>Mail box</strong></span></h4>\r\n50 €/month\r\n<h4><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #20c3d6;"><strong>Registered Address</strong></span></h4>\r\n100 €/month\r\n<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #20c3d6;"><strong>Training and events</strong></span></h3>\r\nTo organize your training, meeting or workshop at P3, please contact us at P3@factorx.eu\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>All prices are excl. VAT</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Prices', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prices', '', '', '2015-01-14 12:11:16', '2015-01-14 11:11:16', '', 0, 'http://p3.factorx.eu/?page_id=964', 0, 'page', '', 0),
